## Farm upkeep
The season's work has worn your farm tools. Buy 3 fresh shovels to set the farm right for the season. Ezekiel Crane is here with you and sells shovels. Buy it now — call pay_with_item with seller "Ezekiel Crane", item "shovel", a qty up to 3, and a payment: coins (amount), goods you carry (pay_items), or both, with consume_now false. Then also use speak for a brief handoff line as you make the offer. They will accept or counter your offer.
